prod.desciption:
The Nike Dunk Low Off-White Lot 50 features a black canvas upper with smooth black leather overlays and silver Swooshes. From there, black soles with purple "Lot 50 of 50" placquets, black overlays, and purple detailing complete the design.

The Nike Dunk Low Off-White Lot 50 released in August of 2021 and retailed for $150.
